</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., male (WAM T77397). 
<emphasis id="B06DD49F918A6E0C2C042C20670EE007" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">A.</emphasis>
Habitus, dorsal view; 
<emphasis id="9ACCE182C3702391D642D8389F50CB4B" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">B.</emphasis>
Habitus, ventral view; 
